{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_CheckThrowBomb}}
'''A_CheckThrowBomb'''<br>
(no parameters)<br>

Decreases the calling actor's health by one point. If it becomes negative or null, the actor is put in its Death state.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|ThrowingBomb}} and derived classes.

[[Category:Decorate Hexen functions]] [[Category:Decorate Restricted functions]]{{DEFAULTSORT:CheckThrowBomb}}
